products.title: Choices Cardigan Stripe Linen Blue Horizon Roller Blind
products.description: Nautical, serene, or full of colour. No matter your scheme, this choices cardigan stripe linen blue horizon roller blind is an outstanding choice. The stripes come in tonal blues, full of energy with a textured look, whilst the fabric is linen mix, for a truly soft and subtle nautical, serene, or full of colour.
